          "text": " is designed to retrieve detailed invoice information from a SQL Server database. It allows filtering based on various parameters such as invoice number, provider ID, group ID, fiscal year, contract ID, billing period, date range, and status ID. The procedure fetches data from multiple tables and views, aggregates certain fields, and formats the output for readability."
